 you can go for it by placing the work desk in the southwest part of such a room. Besides, the northeastern room of your house can be a productive space for those in creative fields such as writing, design and even accountants.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>For entrepreneurs, it\u2019s best if you stick to the southwest, south and west directions for your home office.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>The northwest direction is to be strictly avoided for the work-from-home space at all costs.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161643\/best-direction-as-per-vastu-for-home-office.jpg\" alt=\"Best direction as per vastu for home office where south directions are ideal for placing your work desk\" class=\"wp-image-22644\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161643\/best-direction-as-per-vastu-for-home-office.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161643\/best-direction-as-per-vastu-for-home-office-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161643\/best-direction-as-per-vastu-for-home-office-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161643\/best-direction-as-per-vastu-for-home-office-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Southwest, west and south directions are ideal for placing your work desk, as per Vastu<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Which Is The Best Colour As Per Vastu For Home Office?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Light and neutral colours for your home office create the right atmosphere to help you deliver your best. A cream-coloured palette, for example, will enhance respect and attention towards your work. A soothing green palette brings in positive energy and good vibes. Pastel yellows ensure good health and prosperity, while a pale golden colour means profits and a productive work environment.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Colours to avoid: <\/strong>Dark colours like black and blue.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161633\/best-colour-as-per-vastu-for-home-office.jpg\" alt=\"Best colour as per vastu for home office to go for a productive home office space\" class=\"wp-image-22643\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161633\/best-colour-as-per-vastu-for-home-office.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161633\/best-colour-as-per-vastu-for-home-office-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161633\/best-colour-as-per-vastu-for-home-office-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161633\/best-colour-as-per-vastu-for-home-office-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Light colours are the way to go for a productive home office space<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What Are The Vastu Tips To Consider For The Work Chair And Work Desk?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As per Vastu for home office, your work chair should be sturdy, comfortable and able to support your head too. The work desk must be placed in the southwest direction of the space you&#8217;re occupying for work.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161704\/chair-desk-placed-right-direction-as-per-vastu-shastra.jpg\" alt=\"Vastu tips for home office to consider for the work chair and work desk with a solid chair and a desk placed in the right direction\" class=\"wp-image-22646\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161704\/chair-desk-placed-right-direction-as-per-vastu-shastra.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161704\/chair-desk-placed-right-direction-as-per-vastu-shastra-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161704\/chair-desk-placed-right-direction-as-per-vastu-shastra-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161704\/chair-desk-placed-right-direction-as-per-vastu-shastra-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A solid chair and a desk placed in the right direction are essential as per Vastu Shastra<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Where Should Drawers\/Cabinets Containing Work Papers Be Placed?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The southwest and west directions are ideal for placing drawers, cabinets and the works that store important work-related documents. This placement ensures that these storage units open up facing the north, northeast or east directions, which is ideal per Vastu for home office.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161653\/best-direction-to-place-drawers-cabinets-for-home-office-as-per-vastu.jpg\" alt=\"Best direction to place drawers and cabinets for home office as per vastu\" class=\"wp-image-22645\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161653\/best-direction-to-place-drawers-cabinets-for-home-office-as-per-vastu.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161653\/best-direction-to-place-drawers-cabinets-for-home-office-as-per-vastu-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161653\/best-direction-to-place-drawers-cabinets-for-home-office-as-per-vastu-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161653\/best-direction-to-place-drawers-cabinets-for-home-office-as-per-vastu-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Important work papers at home should be stored in a Vastu-compliant manner<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Keep Your Home Office Clutter-Free<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>There should be no room for unwanted and discarded papers and out-of-order office supplies like pens in your home office. These are believed to bring negative energy into the workspace.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161714\/keep-clean-your-home-office-to-bring-positive-energy.jpg\" alt=\"Keep clean your vastu for home office to bring a positive energy to your home where cluttered and unwanted items are a big no-no \" class=\"wp-image-22647\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161714\/keep-clean-your-home-office-to-bring-positive-energy.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161714\/keep-clean-your-home-office-to-bring-positive-energy-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161714\/keep-clean-your-home-office-to-bring-positive-energy-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161714\/keep-clean-your-home-office-to-bring-positive-energy-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Clutter and unwanted items are a big no-no for the home office<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Additional Vastu Tips To Enhance Your Work-From-Home Experience<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Avoid sitting in front of obstructions like a door or window. Doing so hampers your focus while working.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Placing a water jug in the northeast part of your work desk at home brings in positive energies.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Place a lamp in the southeast part of the workspace, or ensure that this area is well-lit to ensure a productive and efficient workspace.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Avoid using tables with glass tops as your work desk. If you are using your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/dining-room-interiors\/glass-top-dining-table-set\/\">dining table with a glass top<\/a>, for example, ensure that you place a table cover before using it as your workstation.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161734\/vastu-tips-to-enhance-work-from-home-experience.jpg\" alt=\"Other vastu tips to enhance your work-from-home experience with a Small changes to your work-from-home setting\" class=\"wp-image-22649\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161734\/vastu-tips-to-enhance-work-from-home-experience.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161734\/vastu-tips-to-enhance-work-from-home-experience-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161734\/vastu-tips-to-enhance-work-from-home-experience-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/17161734\/vastu-tips-to-enhance-work-from-home-experience-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Small changes to your work-from-home setting can make a big difference<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The home office is here to stay. As per Vastu for home office, these easy-to-follow guidelines will help you create the right environment to be at your best while you work from home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQs On Vastu-compliant home office <\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How can I improve the flow of energy in my Vastu-compliant home office?<\/strong><br>To improve the flow of energy, ensure that your Vastu-compliant home office has plenty of natural light. Avoid dark colors like black or red for the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/home-office-paint-colors\/\">color scheme of the home office<\/a> as they can create a negative energy flow. Place your desk in the south or west direction of the room and face east or north while working.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How can I optimize the lighting in a Vastu-compliant home office?<\/strong><br>Lighting plays a very important role in Vastu Shastra for creating a harmonious and productive environment in your home office. So place your desk near a window to maximize natural light. Place a table lamp on your desk for adequate task lighting. The main light source of the room should be placed in the south or southeast direction. Avoid harsh lights or placing light sources in the northeast corner of the room as it is considered inauspicious.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What kind of colors are suitable for a Vastu-compliant home office?<\/strong><br>For a Vastu-compliant home office, green and blue are the best color options. Both these colors create a cool and calming effect that promotes concentration and focus and improves productivity. Yellow and orange are warm energizing colors that add cheerful and positive vibes to the workspace. Use shades of white like ivory or cream for a soothing and harmonious effect.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What kind of location is best for a Vastu-compliant home office?<\/strong><br>According to the principles of Vastu Shastra, the ideal location for a home office is in the north, east, or northeast direction. This direction is believed to be auspicious and brings prosperity and success to your work. Make sure the entrance to your home office faces the north or east direction.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What kind of artwork and decorations are<\/strong> <strong>appropriate for a Vastu-compliant home office?<\/strong><br>For a Vastu-compliant home office, it is important to choose artwork and decorations that depict positive images and emotions. For artwork, colors such as blue, green, yellow, or other pastel colors are considered ideal. Go for paintings with nature scenes, landscapes, or abstract art that inspires creativity and focus. Choose decor items made from natural materials like wood, stone, or clay.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you enjoyed reading about vastu tips for home office, also explore about <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/basic-vastu-tips-for-home\/\">5 Basic Vastu Tips.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"Work From Home Office Setup Ideas: How To Set Up Your Home Office Before Working #WFH\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/uaukNLpocto?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?